{"tid":1632324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不割蓆」原則，唔只應用於前線，都適用於國際戰線、區議會戰線","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:12.000Z","uid":114801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7aac09e035cbf1956f16b420354cfd4826c76e5","tid":1632324,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"大家好似有個錯覺：「不割蓆」只係單純唔同勇武割蓆<br />\n<br />\n其實國際戰線都一樣，付出左好大努力搞文宣，搞各國遊行。希望手足任何行動都考慮下呢條戰線，國際文宣速度開始追唔上，雖然議員係政治博士班，緊貼香港情況，但投佢地票既選民唔係個個都博士班，議員都要同選民交代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區議會線都一樣，佢地好多都為左狙擊保皇黨，你可以覺得選舉無用。但唔該唔好一句「反正都DQ，哂氣啦」、「食人血饅頭」，就唔理班手足。"},{"pid":"c735674b3df613710cb9a4ccc2a3929c7d31028b","tid":1632324,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港轉咗入大直路啦，唔係依家先黎炒嘛？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632214</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d5a5b78e41a00e049482c297f75ebbcdedaf892","tid":1632324,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"團結一致才能真正解決問題"},{"pid":"cdc1292fad36f220d0eda975d41440ac17d6b7c5","tid":1632324,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"}]}